<br>
If I'm doing archery, I'll keep on shooting arrows to help make it die.<br>
<br>
If I'm in there meleeing and even worse tanking, the first thing I do is duck. This will both turn off auto-attack and disrupt a spell if I was in mid cast. If I want to maintain agro on the mob, I'll chain cast snare to keep it focused on me. If I want to move on to something else, I'll root the thing then back away while the casters finish it with nukes.<br>
<br>
